---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About — Field Notes">
  <h1 class="post-title" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">About</h1>
  <p>
    This is where you tell people who you are, what you do, and why you're
    writing this. Two or three short paragraphs is plenty — nobody expects
    a manifesto.
  </p>
  <p>
    Try covering: what you do for work (in plain language, not a job title
    soup), what you write about here and why, and one honest sentence about
    what you're hoping readers get out of it.
  </p>
  <p>
    <a href="mailto:you@example.com">you@example.com</a> ·
    <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/yourhandle">LinkedIn</a>
  </p>
</Layout>
